[32m+[m[32m## Features[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Zero-click pipeline** — 11 sequential stages from raw Excel workbook to[m
[32m+[m[32m  final figures, driven by a single `python build_group3_model.py` command.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Coupled TH simulation** — transient thermo-hydraulic coupling with[m
[32m+[m[32m  temperature-dependent fluid viscosity and density (linear).[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Adaptive time-stepping** — FEFLOW's FE/BE predictor-corrector scheme with[m
[32m+[m[32m  configurable `dt_initial = 1 × 10⁻¹⁰ d` and `dt_max = 100 d`.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Reliable multi-snapshot access** — a `singleStep()` control loop writes all[m
[32m+[m[32m  20 time-series snapshots to a portable NumPy `.npz` archive, bypassing the[m
[32m+[m[32m  FEFLOW 8.1 IFM DAC enumeration regression.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Multilayer wells (MLW)** — five production wells and five injection wells,[m
[32m+[m[32m  screened across the reservoir interval, with per-well flow rates read from[m
[32m+[m[32m  the workbook.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Seven diagnostic figures** — continuous-field temperature maps[m
[32m+[m[32m  (`tricontourf` on a Delaunay triangulation), breakthrough curves, thermal[m
[32m+[m[32m  power evolution, hydraulic head maps, and adaptive timestep diagnostics.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Parameterised design** — changing four constants in `config.py` adapts the[m
[32m+[m[32m  full pipeline to any of the six course groups.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Licence-free test suite** — 37 pytest tests cover configuration loading,[m
[32m+[m[32m  mesh utilities, thermal power computation, snapshot format, and[m
[32m+[m[32m  post-processing functions; no FEFLOW installation is required to run them.[m
 [m
[31m-A geothermal doublet consists of 5 production wells and 5 injection wells in a[m
[31m-sedimentary reservoir.  Hot water is produced from the reservoir, delivers its[m
[31m-heat to a surface plant, and is reinjected at reduced temperature.  Over the[m
[31m-100-year simulation horizon the cold reinjection plume gradually migrates toward[m
[31m-the production wells (thermal breakthrough), reducing the extractable power.[m
