[32m+[m[32m## Reproducibility[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mA run is deterministic given the same FEFLOW installation, workbook, and[m
[32m+[m[32m`config.py`:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m1. **Initial temperatures** are computed analytically from Fourier's law in[m
[32m+[m[32m   `config.__post_init__()` and cross-checked against the `sliceT` worksheet[m
[32m+[m[32m   at load time. A warning is emitted if any slice deviates by more than[m
[32m+[m[32m   0.05 °C.[m
[32m+[m[32m2. **Hydraulic conductivities** are derived from intrinsic permeabilities via[m
[32m+[m[32m   `_k_to_K()` using fixed reference fluid properties (*ρ* = 999.793 kg/m³,[m
[32m+[m[32m   *μ* = 1.124 × 10⁻³ Pa·s), so no manual unit conversion is required.[m
[32m+[m[32m3. **The NPZ archive** is a portable, self-contained record of the simulation.[m
[32m+[m[32m   All seven figures can be reproduced from it without re-running the[m
[32m+[m[32m   simulation or opening FEFLOW.[m
[32m+[m[32m4. **No stochastic elements** are present in the pipeline. The only source[m
[32m+[m[32m   of numerical non-reproducibility is the FEFLOW solver's internal tolerance[m
[32m+[m[32m   for adaptive step acceptance.[m
